        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "+*Example:*+\n\n*We have:* \n- an ExampleController::indexAction;\n- an url hostname.com\/example&& (with non-alphanumeric characters);\n- a default route\n\n*Result:*\n- Zend_View_Exception: script 'example&&\/index.phtml' not found in path (...script path...)\n\n\n+*Expected result:*+\n- Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Exception: Invalid controller specified (example&&)\n\n+*Description:*+\n- _Zend_Controller_Request_Abstract_ contains an unformated controller name.\n- But _Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Abstract_ format it (remove non-alphanumeric characters in _Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Abstract::_formatName($unformatted, $isAction = false)_).\n\n+*Solution:*+\n- Make a validation instead of a filtering and throw a Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Exception\n\n+*Notes:*+\n- I guess the same thing should be for other parameters (module and action)."
        },
